lead_paragraph: Interim manager Guus Hiddink has expressed surprise that John Terry went public at the weekend with the news Chelsea would not be renewing his contract and believes the defender could yet remain at Stamford Bridge.

headline.print_headline: Chelsea Boss Hiddink Surprised Terry Went Public
